    My main just hit 51 and I'm interested in fiddling with my alt advancement, but I need more info.  Does anyone know a link or site with some info on it? I've looked through Casters, Alka, EQ sites and have found nada.... For instance, I've seen some peps in game with titles like Baron and such, and when I asked them how they got it, they replied with &quot;Put six points into alt advancement&quot; Just wondering how to acomplish this and would like to learn about my other options using this new feature.  Any help would be greatly apriciated =)<br>
